snippet.title: Quar: Battle for Gate 18 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Quar: Battle for Gate 18 is up on Steam! http://store.steampowered.com/app/436940/

Quar: Battle for Gate 18 is a turn-based strategic VR experience set in the grimmsical world of Alwyd! Play through more than a dozen missions with a god's eye view of the battlefield only VR can provide. Can you lead your Quar (ant-eaters with guns and armored vehicles!) to victory and capture Gate 18?

#VirtualReality #VR @HTCVive
